nce, I partake of Fire, I that am grass. And, strange wonder! I am bedewed without being consumed, as the bush of old burned without being consumed. Now with thankful mind, and grateful heart, with thankfulness in my members, my soul and body, I worship a
nd magnify and glorify Thee, my God, for blessed art Thou, both now and unto the ages.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5132266\charrsid9250134 
